				</p>
			</div>
			
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="bg-white bg-opacity-10 rounded-lg p-8 text-center backdrop-blur-sm">
					<div class="text-4xl mb-4">üéí</div>
